item.title: employment
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Op 4 juli vond in Vlaams cultuurhuis de Brakke Grond de 'receptie van de Vlaamse gemeenschap' plaats, een jaarlijkse feestelijke receptie van de Vlaamse Gemeenschap ihkv de Vlaamse feestdag 11 juli. De Brakke Grond was omgetoverd tot een artistieke proeftuin: een aanstekelijke netwerk-setting waar zowel diplomaten als artistiekelingen elkaar binnen semi-gestructureerde context konden ontmoeten.
Zie voor meer informatie: Opdrachtgever: http://www.brakkegrond.nl/ Concept en productie: http://cornelis-serveert.nl/de-vlaamse-proeftuin/ Aangelegenheid: http://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Feestdag_van_Vlaanderen

[/trx_column_item]

[/trx_column_item]

item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
[trx_section box="yes" dedicated="no" scroll="no" top="big" bottom="big"] [trx_title type="2" style="underline" align="center"]We Craft Good Things[/trx_title] [trx_content line_height="30" size="18" align="center" bottom="middle"] Vast experience and understanding of each product’s peculiarities let ThemeRex create outstanding business solutions. [/trx_content] [trx_columns count="3" bottom="middle"] [trx_column_item] [trx_title type="5" align="left" style="iconed" icon="icon-paper-plane-empty" size="large" position="left" background="circle" bottom="5"]TRX Framework[/trx_title] [trx_block dedicated="no" scroll="no" bottom="mini"] ThemeRex worked out an amazing combination of vast fucntionalilty and user’s comfort. [/trx_block] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item] [trx_title type="5" align="left" style="iconed" icon="icon-leaf" size="large" position="left" background="circle" bottom="5"]Clean Modern Code[/trx_title] [trx_block dedicated="no" scroll="no" bottom="mini"] We make the Code of Cluster clean and modern, so that you don't have any troubles intergrating your new website. [/trx_block] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item] [trx_title type="5" align="left" style="iconed" icon="icon-file-image" size="large" position="left" background="circle" bottom="5"]Parallax & Video bgs[/trx_title] [trx_block dedicated="no" scroll="no" bottom="mini"] Absolutely beautiful, Classter is a parallax enabled WordPress theme that includes lots of things to be proud of. [/trx_block] [/trx_column_item] [/trx_columns] [trx_columns count="3"] [trx_column_item] [trx_title type="5" align="left" style="iconed" icon="icon-edit" size="large" position="left" background="circle" bottom="5"]Carefully Crafted Design[/trx_title] [trx_block dedicated="no" scroll="no" bottom="mini"] ThemeRex is doing their best to grant each owner of Classter with the opportunity to present their individuality. [/trx_block] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item] [trx_title type="5" align="left" style="iconed" icon="icon-globe-1" size="large" position="left" background="circle" bottom="5"]100% translatable[/trx_title] [trx_block dedicated="no" scroll="no" bottom="mini"] Classter is 100% translation ready which is why creating different versions of it becomes realy simple. [/trx_block] [/trx_column_item] [trx_column_item] [trx_title type="5" align="left" style="iconed" icon="icon-shopping" size="large" position="left" background="circle" bottom="5"]WooCommerce[/trx_title] [trx_block dedicated="no" scroll="no" bottom="mini"] In case you seek to create an online store, Classter with its WooCommerce integration is the solution. [/trx_block] [/trx_column_item] [/trx_columns] [/trx_section] [trx_section box="no" dedicated="no" scroll="no" color="#ffffff" align="center" top="large"] [trx_testimonials title="Testimonials" controls="on" interval="7000"] [trx_testimonials_item name="Amanda Sitam" position="CEO New York" photo="http://classter.themerex.net/wp-content/imports/2014/12/testimonials_1.jpg"] I downloaded this theme just the other day after spending a few weeks trying to decided between it and a handful of others. Great support with fast and competent responses. Keep up the good work! [/trx_testimonials_item] [trx_testimonials_item name="Marcus Smith" position="Manager, New York" photo="http://classter.themerex.net/wp-content/imports/2014/12/testimonials_2.jpg"] If you are looking for a cv template you are right here. Purchased and surprised about handling and the quick support. highly recommended. [/trx_testimonials_item] [trx_testimonials_item name="Jeniffer King" position="Designer, New York" photo="http://classter.themerex.net/wp-content/imports/2014/12/testimonials_3.jpg"] This theme is top quality. Find an issue? Worry not, because the support that this team provides is amazing! I would definitely recommend this theme for your next project or any other theme from ThemeREX for that matter. [/trx_testimonials_item] [/trx_testimonials] [/trx_section] [trx_section scroll="no" box="yes" top="large" bottom="large" align="center"] [trx_title type="2" bottom="small" align="center"]Selected Clients[/trx_title] [trx_table style="1" size="no_indentation" align="center"]
